data.description: HUGE Price Reduction!! **MOTIVATED SELLER**   This is a MUST-SEE home! Walk across the bridge to enter this architecturally unique and artistic home. It offers up spectacular sunrises and romantic moonrise views from the wall of windows in the great room, not to mention stunning views of the Texas Hill Country as well as seasonal lake views. Go out onto the massive upper deck and have your morning coffee or lay out under the stars with a glass of wine. The secluded master bdrm. is currently downstairs with easy private access to the wading pool in the courtyard. One of the few properties in Briarcliff with over an acre, it’s landscaped with native and drought tolerant plants. Take a walk about and explore the property to find the coolest 2 story treehouse, and the big iron mask sculpture. There is a big stone firepit in the clearing and a chicken-coop just waiting for the feathers to fly! Don’t miss the office/library located off the courtyard. It’s a great home office or a private retreat. Briarcliff offers a large marina, boat ramp, a local restaurant, LOW TAXES, low HOA and the highly ranked Lake Travis ISD.  Bring your imagination and desire to take it all in while relaxing in this one-of-a-kind home.  Just minutes away from Lakeway…Shopping, Dining and great spots for a night out of entertainment! Let the memories begin!  Buyer to verify square footage.  New HVAC in 2021 and new water heater in 2020.
